race.description: Irresistible Pools & Spas Provincial Mdn Plate
race.comment: ODAKA (8) resumes for her third preparation. Ran on late when a respectable fourth over 1100m at Wyong last June. Fitted with the two good trials and a leading rider goes on from the low gate. Respect. BRUTAL ADVANCE (1) has gone under narrowly at his last two starts as favourite. Struck trouble at the start before charging late for a slick second over 1100m at this track. Should be able to hold a position today and may take holding out. ADMIRE ME (6) was slow into stride on debut and worth another look after she finished sixth over 1100m at Gosford. Trained on the track and Schiller sticks. Improver. CINCERITAS (3) Dirty Work gelding from Cinderconi on debut for the Attard barn. Wasn't asked to do much in two trials. Keep safe.
